1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e40636a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630/regulation/38/2/b">38(2)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="c2190861" marker="F34"><p><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e40647a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/3/3/e">Reg. 3(3)(e)</ref> and preceding word inserted (29.4.2013) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e40650a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630">The Universal Credit (Consequential, Supplementary, Incidental and Miscellaneous Provisions) Regulations 2013 (S.I. 2013/630)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e40653a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e40656a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/630/regulation/38/2/b">38(2)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="c2190920" marker="F35"><p>Words in reg. 4(6) inserted (29.7.2013) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e41220a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/1508">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 2) Regulations 2013 (S.I. 2013/1508)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e41223a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/1508/regulation/1/2/a">regs. 1(2)(a)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e41226a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/1508/regulation/3/3/a">3(3)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="c2190922" marker="F36"><p>Words in reg. 4(6) omitted (29.7.2013) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e41237a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/1508">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 2) Regulations 2013 (S.I. 2013/1508)</ref>, 