serted (1.4.2024) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e53999a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/341">The Social Security and Universal Credit (Migration of Tax Credit Claimants and Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2024 (S.I. 2024/341)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54002a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/341/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54005a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/341/regulation/7/3/b">7(3)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-76c777ca24678a0ee2b8f3cb1494eb00" marker="F40"><p>Reg. 6(1A) inserted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(3) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46851a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/1754)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46854a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46857a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754/regulation/4">4</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-91a3a2619f9eee758e12cfca4bcf85ef" marker="F41"><p>Word in reg. 6(1A) substituted (1.4.2017) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47961a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/252">The Universal Credit (Housing Costs Element for claimants aged 18 to 21) (Amendment) Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/252)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47964a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/252/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47967a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/252/regulation/2/2/a">2(2)(a)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47970a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/252/regulation/3">regs. 3</