9855a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2021/1283/regulation/2/1">2(1)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-451d22e5704aa807394aef91380acd25" marker="F104"><p>Reg. 22(3) substituted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2)(3) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44733a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649">The Universal Credit (Work Allowance) Amendment Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/1649)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44736a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44739a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649/regulation/2/3">2(3)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-76dac9653eba62e881b452fc4181a5ad" marker="F105"><p>Reg. 22 table substituted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2)(3) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46869a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649">The Universal Credit (Work Allowance) Amendment Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/1649)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46872a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46875a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1649/regulation/2/4">2(4)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-2e0186fbf2907815e3c3d5c03d0ab88c" marker="F106"><p>Sum in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e55854a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/22">Reg. 22</ref> table  substituted (coming into force in accordance with art. 1(3)(n) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e55857a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2025/295">The Social Security Benefits Up-rating Order 2025 (S.I. 2025/295)</