lation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/1249">The Universal Credit (Childcare Costs and Minimum Income Floor) (Amendment) Regulations 2019 (S.I. 2019/1249)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46003a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/1249/regulation/1/3">regs. 1(3)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46006a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/1249/regulation/2/b">2(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-173591f7deddd5937eec5a3396984fb1" marker="F161"><p>Reg. 34(1)(a) substituted (26.11.2014) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42672a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887">The Universal Credit (Digital Service) Amendment Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/2887)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42675a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42678a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/2/3">2(3)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42681a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/5">reg. 5</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-d725c7e48cde76d40a8fefb03b76fb57" marker="F162"><p>Word in reg. 34(1)(a) (as it has effect both as amended by and apart from the amendment made by SI 2014/2887, reg. 2(3)) substituted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(3) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51182a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/1754)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51185a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51188a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/1754/regulation/6/2">6(2)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Na