/67/regulation/2/1">2(1)</ref><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49893a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/67/regulation/2/2/a">(2)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-38c7e6b970423a24282eb321f9a93954" marker="F195"><p>Words in reg. 53(2)(b) substituted (23.2.2015) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44331a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/67">The Social Security (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/67)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44334a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/67/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44337a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/67/regulation/2/1">2(1)</ref><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44339a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/67/regulation/2/2/b">(2)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-6249ab03f122e0ac6f77343c8287fb59" marker="F196"><p>Reg. 54A inserted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45933a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/345">The Universal Credit (Surpluses and Self-employed Losses) (Digital Service) Amendment Regulations 2015 (S.I. 2015/345)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45936a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/345/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45939a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/345/regulation/2/2">2(2)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45942a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/345/regulation/4">regs. 4</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45945a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2015/345/regulation/5">5</ref>) (as amended by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45949a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/197">S.I. 2017/197</ref>, reg. 2 and <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e45952a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">S.I. 2018/65</ref>, reg. 7)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-7024b2128488f7123fe9f12f4432ebdf" marker="F197"><p>Formula  in reg. 54A(6) substituted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46550a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2021/1283">The Universal Credit (Work Allowance and Taper) (Amendment) Regulations 2021 (S.I. 2021/1283)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46553a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2021/1283/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46556a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2021/1283/regulation/2/2">2(2)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-71326c6ad630f6f5a03ec823701d6ecf" marker="F198"><p>Word in reg. 55(4)(c) omitted (5.4.2015) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46587a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/3255">The Shared Parental Leave and Statutory Shared Parental Pay (Consequential Amendments to Subordinate Legislation) Order 2014 (S.I. 2014/3255)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46590a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/3255/article/1/3">arts. 1(3)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46593a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/3255/article/28/4/a">28(4)(a)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46596a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/3255/article/35/1">art. 35(1)</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-466f976153eaf9d6d198ec9354a0b1f9" marker="F199"><p>Reg. 55(4)(d) omitted (5.4.2015) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44848a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/3255">The Shared Parental Leave and Statutory Shared Parental Pay (Consequential Amendments to Subordinate Legislatio