3/11/b">3(11)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-dd29072ea109dbd3ee290325f99ed2c4" marker="F348"><p>Reg. 99(4A)-(4C) inserted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51464a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2888">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments (No.2) Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/2888)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51467a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2888/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51470a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2888/regulation/8/3/b">8(3)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-421e4bce85e657be6b1e83f1a392e4c0" marker="F349"><p>Words in reg. 99(5) omitted (28.4.2014) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44641a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/597)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44644a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44647a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/2/7/c">2(7)(c)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-086e02584d794100823f678f447d1bb0" marker="F350"><p>Words in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42011a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5">reg. 99(5)</ref> omitted (11.4.2018) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42014a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42017a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4