uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5/b">reg. 99(5)(b)</ref> omitted (11.4.2018) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46089a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46092a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46095a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/11/c/iii/bb">3(11)(c)(iii)(bb)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-34387fb3d9533e2e33f89a2db7e49750" marker="F354"><p>Words in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44025a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5/c">reg. 99(5)(c)</ref> inserted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44028a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44031a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44034a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/11/c/iv">3(11)(c)(iv)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-0c5ef72c96e8f31c38002ec3190fef10" marker="F355"><p><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42158a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5/d">Reg. 99(5)(d)</ref> and word inserted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42161a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42164a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42167a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/11/c/v">3(11)(c)(v)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-bd1b094760340975702e689264d2e739" marker="F356"><p>Reg. 99(5A)(5B) inserted (28.4.2014) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49945a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/597)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49948a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49951a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/2/7/d">2(7)(d)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-3fe92fd1ca85891db29aee3733257f1d" marker="F357"><p>Words in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44502a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5A">reg. 99(5A)</ref> substituted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44505a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44508a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44511a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/11/d">3(11)(d)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-ff8bf8583fb6d9771ffb70bf0af7a4ca" marker="F358"><p>Words in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e53160a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/5B/a">reg. 99(5B)(a)</ref> substituted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e53163a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e53166a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e53169a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/11/d">3(11)(d)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-63732940d1758e76e37d852e517c1fdd" marker="F359"><p><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46052a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/6">Reg. 99(6)</ref>  substituted (26.9.2022) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46055a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2022/886">The Universal Credit (Administrative Earnings Threshold) (Amendment) Regulations 2022 (S.I. 2022/886)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46058a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2022/886/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e46061a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2022/886/regulation/2">2</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-aa295e3c0b6ccf9e7b92a741d6ef510a" marker="F360"><p>Words in <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54198a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/99/6/a">reg. 99(6)(a)</ref> substituted (13.5.2024) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54201a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/536">The Universal Credit (Administrative Earnings Threshold) (Amendment) (No. 2) Regulations 2024 (S.I. 2024/536)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54204a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/536/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e54207a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/536/regulation/2/a">2(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentar