sic5-d3e51709a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/regulation/1/2/a">reg. 1(2)(a)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51712a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/schedule/5/paragraph/5/e/i">Sch. 5 para. 5(e)(i)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-808e19757f85f266221eee4429e65e95" marker="F395"><p>Sch. 1 para. 3(h) added (3.11.2014) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47314a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771">The Housing Benefit and Universal Credit (Supported Accommodation) (Amendment) Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/771)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47317a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771/regulation/1/3">regs. 1(3)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47320a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771/regulation/2/2/b/ii">2(2)(b)(ii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-add8def90250e4d516803ee3abfb2a88" marker="F396"><p>Sch. 1 para. 3(i) inserted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49205a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49208a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49211a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/12/a">3(12)(a)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49214a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/2">reg. 8(2)</ref><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49216a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/3">(3)</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-383bbaa6e7d9405dd65e5a12879a461e" marker="F397"><p>Sch. 1 para. 3A inserted (3.11.2014) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44252a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771">The Housing Benefit and Universal Credit (Supported Accommodation) (Amendment) Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/771)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44255a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771/regulation/1/3">regs. 1(3)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e44258a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/771/regulation/2/2/c">2(2)(c)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-b4b3a6b94463ff24a2847550fec2ff3a" marker="F398"><p>Sch. 1 para. 3B inserted (11.4.2018) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49578a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49581a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49584a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/12/b">3(12)(b)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49587a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/2">reg. 8(2)</ref><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e49589a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/3">(3)</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-1846027a389186f6ee377a814d4455e9" marker="F399"><p>Sch. 1 paras. 4-6 omitted (with effect in accordance with regs. 19 - 21 of the amending S.I.) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42728a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725">The Loans for Mortgage Interest Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/725)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42731a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/regulation/1/2/a">reg. 1(2)(a)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42734a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/schedule/5/paragraph/5/e/ii">Sch. 5 para. 5(e)(ii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-0efce00c5983310433ed686ce0c63b90" marker="F400"><p>Words in Sch. 1 para. 7(3)(a) substituted (with effect in accordance with regs. 19 - 21 of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42239a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725">The Loans for Mortgage Interest Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/725)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42242a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/regulation/1/2/a">reg. 1(2)(a)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e42245a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/schedule/5/paragraph/5/e/iii">Sch. 5 para. 5(e)(iii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-84a80ce09d06a804e9cf520e458b7812" marker="F401"><p>Words in Sch. 1 para. 8(1)(a) omitted (11.4.2018) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47464a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47467a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4">regs. 1(4)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47470a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/12/c">3(12)(c)</ref> (with <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47473a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/2">reg. 8(2)</ref><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47475a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/3">(3)</ref>)</p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-40eaba3b0e32a333bf8250e3602a34da" marker="F402"><p><ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3