 effect in accordance with reg. 1(2) of the amending S.I.) by virtue of <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51689a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213">The Housing Benefit and Universal Credit (Size Criteria) (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/213)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51692a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e51695a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/regulation/6/b/ii">6(b)(ii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-d0333aed55e4b0bc94b144bb5e1077c0" marker="F427"><p>Sch. 4 para. 12(1)(d) and semi-colon inserted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e50923a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213">The Housing Benefit and Universal Credit (Size Criteria) (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/213)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e50926a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e50929a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/regulation/6/b/iii">6(b)(iii)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-870742e2430c92be03da48b915953b06" marker="F428"><p>Sch. 4 para. 12(2) substituted (with effect in accordance with reg. 1(2) of the amending S.I.) by <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47546a1310" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213">The Housing Benefit and Universal Credit (Size Criteria) (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/213)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47549a1310" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</ref>, <ref eId="rnb8sic5-d3e47552a1310" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/213/reg